Package: hitandrun
Type: Package
Title: "Hit and Run" for Sampling Uniformly From Convex Shapes
Version: 0.4-3
Date: 2014-XX-YY
Author: Gert van Valkenhoef, Tommi Tervonen
Maintainer: Gert van Valkenhoef <g.h.m.van.valkenhoef@rug.nl>
Description: The "Hit and Run" Markov Chain Monte Carlo (MCMC) method for sampling uniformly from convex shapes defined by linear constraints. Includes specialized functions for sampling normalized weights with arbitrary linear constraints.
URL: http://github.com/gertvv/hitandrun
License: GPL-3
